title: A manhunt is underway for a gunman in Pennsylvania suburb shooting
description: Police have issued a shelter-in-place orders in Falls Township,  a Pennsylvania suburb near Trenton, N.J., as authorities search for the shooter.

title: Opinion: Animals have overtaken our lives, and we're having a wonderful time
description: NPR's Scott Simon muses on his family's life with animals — a dog, a foster cat, a hamster in a hamster ball — and all that entails.

title: An older Boeing plane found with missing panel after landing in Oregon
description: A post-flight inspection revealed a missing panel on an Boeing 737-800 that had just arrived at its destination in southern Oregon on Friday after flying from San Francisco, officials said.
